videos.description: Kansas State RB Jordon Brown takes the handoff, finds the hole and muscles across the goal line for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kansas State's Brown finds a hole for the score) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kansas State's Brown finds a hole for the score

videos.description: Mississippi State QB Tommy Stevens lobs a 35-yard pass into the end zone to WR Osirus Mitchell who hauls in the TD with one hand.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mississippi State's Mitchell makes one-handed TD grab) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mississippi State's Mitchell makes one-handed TD grab

videos.description: Mississippi State QB Garrett Shrader decides to run the ball himself and finds his way in for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mississippi State's Shrader keeps it himself for TD) 2019/09/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mississippi State's Shrader keeps it himself for TD

videos.description: Kansas State's Malik Knowles fields the kickoff at the goal line and speeds 100 yards downfield for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Kansas State's Knowles returns kickoff 100 yards for TD

videos.description: Kansas State QB Skylar Thompson throws a 15-yard touchdown pass to WR Dalton Schoen to give the Wildcats the lead.

videos.headline: Kansas State's Thompson finds Schoen for go-ahead score
